divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking my trash can to the curb when this pulsating star like light caught my eye. I watched thinking it could be a plane when I saw there were two objects, one atop the other. I went and got some binoculars and could see the objects were pulsating with several color of lights. I went inside got my wife and she saw the same objects.
Summary: pulsating lights (2) one above the other. stationary
